[I] Bidirectional backup/sync tool

[T] Unison is a bidirectional networked backup and synchronisation tool written
[T] in Ocaml. It uses ideas from cvs, rsync, the coda filesystem and is capable
[T] of securing the transfer using a ssh tunnel.

[U] https://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bcpierce/unison/

